Interface PropertyMappingVectorFieldOptionsStep

All Superinterfaces:
PropertyMappingFieldOptionsStep<PropertyMappingVectorFieldOptionsStep>, PropertyMappingStep
@Incubating public interface PropertyMappingVectorFieldOptionsStep extends PropertyMappingFieldOptionsStep<PropertyMappingVectorFieldOptionsStep>
The step in a property-to-index-field mapping where optional parameters can be set, when the index field is a vector field.
